relevant_findings.general: Awake, alert, NAD (no acute distress), pleasant, appropriate, cooperative.
relevant_findings.heent: NCAT (normocephalic, atraumatic), PERRL (pupils equal, round, reactive to light), EOMI (extraocular movements intact), no scleral icterus, MMM (moist mucous membranes).
relevant_findings.neck: Supple, no significant JVD (jugular venous distention) or carotid bruits appreciated.
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Lungs CTA (clear to auscultation) bilaterally, no wheezes, ronchi, or rales.
relevant_findings.cardiac: Regular rate, normal S1 S2, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops appreciated.
relevant_findings.abdomen: Tenderness to palpation (TTP) in pelvic area, soft, non-distended (ND), normoactive bowel sounds, no masses or organomegaly noted, no rebound tenderness or rosvig's sign.
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, 2+ radial and dorsalis pedis (DP) pulses bilaterally.
